    <briefdescription>
<para>A wrapper around KisIntParseSpinBox, which is a cleverer SpinBox, able to parse arithmetic expressions. The widget itself is accessed with the <ref refid="class_int_parse_spin_box_1a3abd6b87dbdeecb9bd0039b2062be8ea" kindref="member">widget()</ref> function. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Use this spinbox instead of the basic one from Qt if you want it to be able to parse arithmetic expressions. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
